data.description: CLOSE-IN Charming, Updated Tri-Level Home in quiet community. Feel like you live in the country yet so close to all conveniences. This remodeled 3 Bedroom, 2.25 Bath Home features a newer roof, newer windows, all new flooring & trim, all new interior paint, new smart automatic irrigation system, renovated kitchen with new countertops/cooktop/sink/dishwasher, upgraded lighting, new doors, new toilets & so much more! Two Living Areas, kitchen fit for entertaining that connects to your deck, utility room, & 2-car attached garage w/ ample storage space. Property includes two parcels and has an amazingly oversized backyard. Must see to appreciate. Sold AS-IS. One Year Home Warranty included. Welcome Home!
